Name: Monster Logic
About the game: Use, edit and organize monsters on a game grid to create a path to send the appropriate cans to the cute bat monster. Be sure not to make mistakes, he has a temper. Features Based on esoteric programming languages Befunge and Trefunge 42 unique levels 7 Hand-drawn biomes 13 different monsters Harder Dark World levels Compete online with your friends, the world and even the dev!
